Code was added to the original LSM6DS Library

Adafruit_LSM6DS.h
```
/**************************************************************************/
/*!
    @brief Check for available data from accelerometer and gyroscope
    @returns 1 if available, 0 if not
*/
int Adafruit_LSM6DS::accelerationGyroscopeAvailable(void) {
  return (this->status() & 0x03) ? 1 : 0;
}
```


